<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:14:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>高管表示，沙特阿美仍在寻求交易，同时将雷诺-吉利发动机合资公司的股份维持在 10%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/aramco-still-pursuing-deals-while-keeping-renault-geely-engine-jv-stake-10-2024-09-03/</link><description>一位高级管理人员告诉路透社，国家控股的石油公司沙特阿美公司不打算增加其在燃油发动机合资企业 Horse Powertrain 中 10% 的股份，同时将继续寻求更多交易以扩大其下游业务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:05:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/aramco-still-pursuing-deals-while-keeping-renault-geely-engine-jv-stake-10-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>汤加领导人表示警察提供“免于恐惧的自由”并支持民主</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tonga-leader-says-police-provide-freedom-fear-support-democracy-2024-09-03/</link><description>汤加总理索瓦莱尼周二在向太平洋岛屿警察局长发表讲话时强调了警察在民主国家提供“免于恐惧的自由”方面的作用，并指出全球主要大国对该地区的关注日益增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 07:18:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tonga-leader-says-police-provide-freedom-fear-support-democracy-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>印度尼西亚依靠荷兰出生的球队寻求重返世界杯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/indonesia-lean-dutch-born-contingent-quest-world-cup-return-2024-09-03/</link><description>印度尼西亚近 90 年来首次参加世界杯的挑战呈现出明显的荷兰风味，申泰勇的球队周四对阵沙特阿拉伯，希望点燃人们期待已久的重返足球最伟大舞台的梦想。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 07:18:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/indonesia-lean-dutch-born-contingent-quest-world-cup-return-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国东部校车撞死学生和家长 11人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/eleven-dead-after-school-bus-hits-students-parents-eastern-china-2024-09-03/</link><description>据中央电视台报道，周二，中国东部山东省一辆校车在繁忙的人行横道失控，造成 11 人死亡，令人不安的画面显示，尸体躺在路上，并被困在车底下。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 06:58:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/eleven-dead-after-school-bus-hits-students-parents-eastern-china-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>8月特斯拉中国销量创年内最佳</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-sales-have-best-month-year-august-2024-09-03/</link><description>特斯拉在中国的销量 8 月份创下了今年以来最好的月份，这家美国电动汽车制造商受益于较小城市的强劲销售。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 05:35:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-sales-have-best-month-year-august-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>由于高利率的影响，中国数字平台Qifa推迟了莫斯科IPO</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-digital-platform-qifa-delays-moscow-ipo-high-interests-rates-bite-2024-09-03/</link><description>专注于俄罗斯和中国之间贸易的数字平台 Qifa 创始人孙天舒周二告诉路透社，由于俄罗斯高利率和充满挑战的商业环境，该平台推迟了在莫斯科交易所的首次公开募股。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 05:18:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-digital-platform-qifa-delays-moscow-ipo-high-interests-rates-bite-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>“香港47”：法院结束香港最大国家安全案件的减刑听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-47-court-wraps-up-mitigation-hearing-citys-largest-national-security-2024-09-03/</link><description>周二，最后一批 45 名香港活动人士在一次具有里程碑意义的国家安全审判中提出了最后的减刑请求，罪名是“阴谋颠覆国家政权”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 04:53:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-47-court-wraps-up-mitigation-hearing-citys-largest-national-security-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>美国气候特使波德斯塔将于周三访华会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/top-us-climate-diplomat-podesta-visit-china-sept-4-6-2024-09-03/</link><description>中国环境部表示，美国气候特使约翰·波德斯塔将从周三开始访问中国，为期三天，讨论气候变化问题，世界上两个最大的温室气体排放国希望弥合在金融等问题上的分歧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 04:43:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/top-us-climate-diplomat-podesta-visit-china-sept-4-6-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，特斯拉计划推出六座 Model Y，预计 2025 年在中国生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-plans-six-seat-model-y-production-slated-2025-china-sources-say-2024-09-03/</link><description>两名知情人士表示，特斯拉计划从 2025 年底开始在中国生产 Model Y 汽车的六座版本，这家美国汽车制造商正在努力提高其最畅销但已过时的电动汽车（EV）的吸引力。 ）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 04:22:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-plans-six-seat-model-y-production-slated-2025-china-sources-say-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾热带风暴“八木”造成的死亡人数上升至13人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-death-toll-tropical-storm-yagi-rises-13-2024-09-03/</link><description>菲律宾至少有 13 人因热带风暴“八木”而死亡，周二，马尼拉和附近省份的学校和政府办公室因预期的恶劣天气而关闭。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 02:39:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-death-toll-tropical-storm-yagi-rises-13-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>投资者等待美国数据，世界股市走低，美元坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-03/</link><description>世界股市周二持稳，美元仍接近两周高点，因投资者在等待可能决定美国降息幅度的一系列经济数据变得谨慎。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 02:25:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国需求担忧盖过利比亚出口暂停，油价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-fall-weak-demand-overshadows-libya-blockade-2024-09-03/</link><description>布伦特油价周二下跌，原因是全球最大原油进口国中国经济增长疲软加剧了需求担忧，而利比亚生产和出口的停止提供了支撑。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 02:16:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-fall-weak-demand-overshadows-libya-blockade-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>泡菜不再了吗？气候变化使韩国最受欢迎的卷心菜面临风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/kimchi-no-more-climate-change-puts-south-koreas-beloved-cabbage-dish-risk-2024-09-03/</link><description>韩国著名的泡菜正在成为气候变化的受害者，科学家、农民和制造商表示，由于气温上升，用于制作这种随处可见的菜肴的腌制大白菜的质量和数量受到影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 01:19:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/kimchi-no-more-climate-change-puts-south-koreas-beloved-cabbage-dish-risk-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>美元小幅触及两周高位；日元重新成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-brace-labour-data-deluge-2024-09-03/</link><description>周二美元徘徊在接近两周高点附近，因投资者准备迎接一系列经济数据，包括周五的美国就业数据，这些数据可能会影响美联储预期的降息规模。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 01:15:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-brace-labour-data-deluge-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国和南非同意寻求平衡贸易和更多投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-south-africa-sign-cooperation-documents-trade-more-investments-2024-09-03/</link><description>周二的一份联合声明显示，中国和南非的最高领导人在北京会面，同意促进平衡贸易，并讨论促进工商界之间的双向投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 00:07:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-south-africa-sign-cooperation-documents-trade-more-investments-2024-09-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>